      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "2 cpu, 4 GB RAM --> upgrade it 8 CPU, 16 GB RAM --> Vertical Scaling\n\n--> vertical scaling required you to stop the ec2 instance.\n\n** Problem With Vertical Scaling : OS/HW/AZ Failure takes our app down\n\n\n\n\n",
